{"tid":1506101,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實支那呢個term係侮辱民國時期嘅中國人","createTime":"2019-08-25T17:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T07:53:46.000Z","uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e66002546d799861bab92cc705487dea4157baf0","tid":1506101,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:03:49.000Z","msg":"支那呢個term古代已經有 去到民國時期先出現貶意 <br />\n點解用呢隻字屌共產中國啲人會有反應<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又或者點解中華民國台灣人會覺得無野 唔多明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310a8c68d4ac5802d5d524e856b161dcf07be684","tid":1506101,"uid":189157,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:05:32.000Z","msg":"因為佢地係台灣人<br />\n我地係香港人<br />\n係得支那人先會care支那呢個term"},{"pid":"dc55adfd306f692746dd9e9a7bdb0bf1be514025","tid":1506101,"uid":185712,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:16:28.000Z","msg":"你試下對住台灣人罵佢支那人 睇下佢屌唔屌7你"},{"pid":"4592b054c90bea27b8420144edf83fdcab24d765","tid":1506101,"uid":275370,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T17:17:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F4Okr8U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF4Okr8U.jpg&h=60947c16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5f23ecb3b97d9e6b0f479f70c6499e843e7d43e7","tid":1506101,"uid":173598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"dc55adfd